twitch_info.title: CN3 F100 grind day ?? + 6
twitch_info.description: Holy double PB batman! I managed to do the first blue jump offscreen and then practiced the heck out of it before this stream. Managed to do it twice in a row, and PB'd both times, first time did the water jump but died before touching the vine. Second time I touched the vine but died on the way up from the apple. Finished out The Dear Hunter's Color Spectrum album. Good stuff.
